un]]<br />[[Noh Sa-yeon]]<br />[[Rowoon]] ([[SF9 (band)|SF9]])}}\n| [[Seoul Broadcasting System|SBS Tanhyeon-dong Production Center]]<br />{{small|([[Ilsan|Ilsanseo-gu]], [[Goyang]], [[Gyeonggi-do]])}}\n| Comedian Team<br/>{{small|(Yoo Jae-suk, Ji Suk-jin, Yang Se-chan, Jo Se-ho)}}<br />Singer Team<br />{{small|(Haha, Kim Jong-kook, Hong Jin-young, Noh Sa-yeon)}}<br />Actor Team<br />{{small|(Lee Kwang-soo, Song Ji-hyo, Lee Do-hyun, Rowoon)}}\n| Spy Team<br/>{{small|(Yoo Jae-suk, Kim Jong-kook, Lee Do-hyun)}}\n| '''Mission Team's mission'''<br/>Identify and Apprehend at least 2 spies, and be the one with the most prize sticks at the end of the race<br/>'''Spy Team's mission'''<br />Stamp the prize sticks and be the one with the most prize sticks at the end of the race\n| Spy Team '''Wins'''<br/>{{small|Yoo Jae-suk, Kim Jong-kook and Lee Do-hyun gets 3 chances each to pick a random prize. Yoo Jae-suk receives Ji Suk-jin's pillow and Kim Jong-kook's massage, Kim Jong-kook receives a 10 dollar gift card while Lee Do-hyun receives a premium wet wipes pack and a gold bar.}}\n|-\n|}\n\n== Upcoming episodes ==\n{{clear}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! style=\"background: #BFCCFF\" width=\"100\" |{{abbr|Ep.|Episode}}\n! style=\"background: #BFCCFF\" width=\"70\"| Airdate<br />{{small|(Filming date)}}\n! style=\"background: #BFCCFF\"| Title\n! style=\"background: #BFCCFF; width:140px\"| Guest(s)\n! style=\"background: #BFCCFF\" width=\"100\"| Landmark\n! style=\"background: #BFCCFF\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"320\"| Teams\n! style=\"background: #BFCCFF; width:170px\"| Mission\n|-\n!500<br /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://mstoo.asiae.co.kr/article.php?aid=63643813523&naver=1|title=[\ub2e8\ub3c5] '\ub7f0\ub2dd\ub9e8' 500\ud68c \ud2b9\uc9d1, \uc5d0\uc774\ud551\ud06cX\uccad\ud558X\ub7ec\ube14\ub9ac\uc988X\uc704\ud0a4\ubbf8\ud0a4 \ucd9c\uaca9|website=Sports Today|access-date=April 14, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/2